<html>
  <head>
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7fa; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 5px
      15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); } .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom:
      30px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; } .logo {
      margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; }
      .header h1 { color: #2c3e50; margin: 0; font-weight: 600; } .content {
      font-size: 16px; color: #444; } .booking-details { background-color:
      #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left:
      4px solid #3498db; } .booking-details p { margin: 8px 0; display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between; } .booking-details strong { color:
      #2c3e50; } .booking-id { font-size: 18px; color: #3498db; margin-bottom:
      15px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; } .cta-button { display:
      block; text-align: center; margin: 30px auto; } .cta-button a {
      background-color: #3498db; color: white; padding: 12px 30px;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 30px; font-weight: 600; display:
      inline-block; transition: background-color 0.3s; } .cta-button a:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9; } .footer { text-align: center; margin-top:
      30px; font-size: 14px; color: #888; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px
      solid #eaeaea; } .contact-info { display: flex; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px; } .contact-info span { margin: 0 10px; } .thank-you {
      text-align: center; margin: 25px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #2c3e50; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <div class='logo'>InnkeeperPro</div>
        <h1>Booking Confirmation</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing InnkeeperPro for your upcoming stay. We're
          excited to host you and make your visit special!</p>

        <div class='booking-id'>Booking ID: {{bookingId}}</div>

        <div class='booking-details'>
          <p><span>Hotel:</span> <strong>{{hotelName}}</strong></p>
          <p><span>Check-In:</span> <strong>{{checkIn}}</strong></p>
          <p><span>Check-Out:</span> <strong>{{checkOut}}</strong></p>
          <p><span>Room Type:</span> <strong>{{roomType}}</strong></p>
          <p><span>Room Number:</span> <strong>{{roomNumber}}</strong></p>
          <p><span>Status:</span> <strong>{{status}}</strong></p>
        </div>

        <p>Your reservation is confirmed and we're looking forward to welcoming
          you. If you need to make any changes to your booking, please contact
          us at least 24 hours before your scheduled check-in.</p>

        <div class='cta-button'>
          <a href='https://innkeeperpro.com/my-bookings/{{bookingId}}'>View
            Booking Details</a>
        </div>

        <div class='thank-you'>
          We look forward to hosting you!
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <div class='contact-info'>
          <span>üìû 08150442746</span>
          <span>‚úâÔ∏è support@innkeeperpro.com</span>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; 2025 InnkeeperPro. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>